			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1680883">
									

<p>There is some vital information missing here. Most importantly, are the contained specimens the only population, or are there others loose in the world? Is there a MTF assigned to locate any un-contained instances? How many individuals are in containment? Do they breed in captivity, and if not, what conditions are required for reproduction? If the animal can bore through windows and walls, what is the extent of this ability? Is brick enough to keep them out? Can they penetrate certain metals?</p>
